{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"109714-come-stay-with-me","title":"Come Stay With Me","description":"Tendai Turtle’s Granny has hurt her shell and Mum and Dad have to go to help her. 'Come stay with me,'says Tendai’s best friend Busi Bunny, and the fun begins.","language":"English","langCode":"en","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Nasrin Siege"],"illustrators":["Subi Bosa"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Book Dash","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/109714-come-stay-with-me"},"cover":{"card":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/527479/size3/c27aed7bef82c0d48e6c6bbfd3c447fd.jpg","large":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/527479/size6/c27aed7bef82c0d48e6c6bbfd3c447fd.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/181314/size6/8e193e621b6f7760c3b9a607e6e80662.jpg","text":"Tendai Turtle lives in the water.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/181316/size6/e88ab1f218df4ac5dddfbc863e9b4105.jpg","text":"Tendai’s best friend is Bunny Busi. She lives in a tree.","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/181328/size6/78eb679820eaccaff8dac8708af5c23f.jpg","text":"Granny Turtle has hurt her shell.","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/181330/size6/340ee26ff45ebe01989b3d3d642192a5.jpg","text":"“We have to go to help Granny,” says Mum.","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/181331/size6/ac6907a8c0dbe37dabbb677b7e3a3b6e.jpg","text":